Start by using your left hand to play the chord for 1976, then your right hand to play the notes for the ice level over that period. 

When the line goes up, play a higher note. 
When it points down, play a lower note.
Then, when you reach 1984, play the chord in your left hand again, and play the notes for the next 8 years. 

Keep going, until you reach the end of the chart.
